CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper October 1, 1960, pg. 18, reads: "Winners - There were plenty of victory smiles at the Centre Avenue YMCA last Friday night during the first All-Star amateur boxing show of the season. Photo on the left shows Joe Wright of the Daniels A. C. having his hands raised after he scored a tko over Porkey Cragget. On the far left is Charlie Daniels, matchmaker, and on the right is Bob Edwards, Centre Avenue 'Y' physical director... - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Charlie Daniels and Bob Edwards standing on either side of boxer Joe Wright after victorious match against Porkey Cragget at All-Star amateur boxing show, Centre Avenue YMCA
